River Plate won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:                             

Estudiantes LPG          Gabriel Mario Ogando; Eduardo Enrique Rodríguez, 
                         Nicolás Palma; Héctor Blotto, Saúl Ongaro, Eduardo 
                         Sande; Julio Aurelio Gómez, Juan José Negri, Ángel 
                         Ricardo Laferrara, Carlos José Cirico, Manuel Gregorio 
                         Pelegrina.
                         
River Plate              Julio Barrios; Ricardo Alfredo Vaghi, Avelino Cadilla; 
                         Norberto Antonio Yácono, Bruno Rodolfi, José Ramos; 
                         Juan Carlos Muñoz, José Manuel Moreno, Adolfo Alfredo 
                         Pedernera, Ángel Amadeo Labruna, Carlos Desiderio 
                         Peucelle.
                         
Referee                  Leopoldo Amoroso.

Tickets                  13,000 tickets.

